OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMore pupils off school ill 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas flu cases rise          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Absence rates across schools in England
OL,6, rose sharply at the start of December  
OL,7, as more pupils missed class due to     
OL,8, illness, official figures suggest.     
OL,10,FThe proportion of children off sick    
OL,11,Frose to 7.5% in the week commencing 5  
OL,12,FDecember - up from 6.1% the previous   
OL,13,Fweek and 2.6% at the start of the term.
OL,15,FOverall absence rates up to that week  
OL,16,Fsurpassed the whole of the 2021 autumn 
OL,17,Fterm, when Omicron was taking hold.    
OL,19,FA head teachers' union said it was     
OL,20,F"concerning" for health and education. 
